    "created_at": "2017-04-28T15:50:57Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-04-28T15:50:57Z",
    "body": "For this problem, our app uses a workaround by using `restore` event and `screen` module.\r\n\r\nThe concept is below. \r\n\r\n```javascript\r\nwin.on('restore', () => {\r\n  const isOffScreen = offScreenValidation(win);\r\n  if(isOffScreen) {\r\n    win.setPosition(0, 0);\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```"
